rows.label: tlk41100171_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Is the Goddess of the Holy See
a goddess of fortune, do you think?

rows.label: tlk41100171_02_msg0002
rows.name:
There're tourists who toss coins over
the edge at Milama Viewpoint, but a lot
of them actually land around here.

rows.label: tlk41100171_02_msg0003
rows.name:
And there's been more than usual with
the whole funeral business. I should
thank the goddess for that, I suppose!
